        "subject": "LU-333: read_bytes in llite/*/stats should report bytes read.",
        "message": "LU-333: read_bytes in llite/*/stats should report bytes read.\n\nRequesting a large number of bytes to be read from a small or empty\nfile causes inflated values in llite/*/read_bytes.  The problem is\nthat the LPROC_LL_READ_BYTES stat is tallied by the umber of bytes\nrequested rather than the number of bytes actually read.\n\nChange-Id: I429ef6e8f4361b69927abd2be894c7771c09d64b\nSigned-off-by: John Hammond <jhammond@tacc.utexas.edu>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
